data.name: guna2HtmlLabel2.Text
data.value:
You can specify up to 8 applications in which you do not want HovText to be active in. This could be in e.g. a password manager or in "problematic" applications like Microsoft Excel. Please view the Documentation on how to fill in the details.

HovText will not do any processing in the below listed applications.

data.name: UiFeedbackLabelIntro.DefaultText
data.value: If you have any feedback for the developer, then please reach out, as I would appreciate some interaction with the users of HovText :-) Maybe you want to ask a question, suggest a feature or file a bug report? Your feedback will only be visible for the developer.

data.name: UiAboutLabelText.Text
data.value:
This application is open source, and you can use it on any computer free of charge. You are of course encouraged to donate some $$$, if you find it useful and want to motivate for continues support :-) All donations received will be used solely for enhancing HovText.

Since HovText has a very small user base, another way to contribute is by writing a review or comment about it online to help spread the word. One comment from a real user is worth more than many comments from the developer ;-)

Please note that it is not permitted to sell or distribute the application for any commercial purposes without explicit written consent from the developer.

You can visit the HovText home page here:
https://hovtext.com
Kind regards,

Jesper and Dennis
